    dc:creator "Prokhorov, Alexey V.; Gubin, Oleksandr I." ;
    dc:date "2019" ;
    dc:title "Description of the larva of Meliboeus morawitzi (Semenov, 1905) (Coleoptera: Buprestidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3449049>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3449047>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3449051>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3449053>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3449057>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3449059> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3449049>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9–17. Meliboeus morawitzi (Semenov, 1905), mature larva. 9 Habitus, dorsal view; 10 Epistome with labrum, dorsal view; 11 Labrum, dorsal view (aals: apical anterolateral seta, das: dorsal anterior seta, dps: dorsal posterior seta, ss: subapical seta, vs: ventral seta); 12 Labio-maxillary complex, external surface (c: cardo, s: stipes, mp1: first segment of maxillary palpi, mp2 the second segment of maxillary palpi, p: prementum); 13 Right antenna, dorsolateral view (ts: trichosensillum, sa: sensory appendage, ps: palmate sensilla, bs: basiconic sensilla); 14 Right mandible, dorsal view (upper arrow shows the edge of penicillium, lower arrow shows the seta attachment); 15 Right mandible, lateral view (arrow shows the small tooth on the inner side of mandible); 16 Prementum, external surface; 17 Prementum and maxillary palp, internal surface (ma: mala, p: prementum)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3449049/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3449047>
    dc:description "FIGURES 3–8. Larvae of Meliboeus, details of structure. 3–6 M. morawitzi (Semenov, 1905), mature larva: 3 Epistome with labrum, dorsal view (l: labrum, ac: anteclypeus, es: epistomal sensilla); 4 Labrum, dorsal view (aals: apical anterolateral seta, das: dorsal anterior seta, dps: dorsal posterior seta, ss: subapical seta, vs: ventral seta); 5 Right antenna, dorsolateral view (ts: trichosensillum, sa: sensory appendage, ps: palmate sensilla, bs: basiconic sensilla); 6 Prementum with apical setae of corner sclerites and microsetal area; 7 Prementum of M. graminis (Panzer, 1799), 8 Prementum of M. subulatus (Morawitz, 1861)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3449047/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3449051>
    dc:description "FIGURES 18–21. Meliboeus morawitzi (Semenov, 1905), mature larva. 18 Pronotal plate of prothorax; 19 Pronotal grooves; 20 Prosternal plate of prothorax; 21 Prosternal groove." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3449051/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3449053>
    dc:description "FIGURES 22–25. Meliboeus morawitzi (Semenov, 1905), mature larva. 22 Mesothoracic spiracle; 23 Abdominal apex with terminal processes, dorsal view (setae not shown); 24 Terminal processes of anal segment, lateral view; 25 Abdominal spiracle (segment 2)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3449053/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3449057>
    dc:description "FIGURES 26–31. Meliboeus graminis (Panzer, 1799), mature larva. 26 Epistome with labrum, dorsal view; 27 Labrum, dorsal view; 28 Pronotal plate of prothorax; 29 Prosternal plate of prothorax; 30 Labio-maxillary complex, external surface; 31 Prementum, external surface." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3449057/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3449059>
    dc:description "FIGURES 32–37. Meliboeus subulatus (Morawitz, 1861), mature larva. 32 Epistome with labrum, dorsal view; 33 Labrum, dorsal view; 34 Pronotal plate of prothorax; 35 Prosternal plate of prothorax; 36 Labio-maxillary complex, external surface; 37 Prementum, external surface (arrow shows posterior border of microsetal area with deep median notch)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3449059/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

